<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> Kempnater, als wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erbe<ex>r</ex>keit</expan> nechst
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Rumels
                        des <expan>elt<ex>er</ex>n,</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s,</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n,</ex></expan> wie das er uns
                            <expan>fürgeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab, daz im
                            <expan>lantma<ex>n</ex>sweise</expan> gesagt sey
                            <expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz er und die
                            <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan> und ire güter vor euch und den
                                <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>unsich<ex>er</ex></expan> sein <add>etc</add>., derselb bot euch
                        desmals nicht <add>daheim</add> getroffen <add>hat</add> noch uns kein
                                <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> darauf
                                <add><expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan> ist</add>. Also
                                <expan>ro<ex>gamus,</ex></expan> daz ir <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>ern</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<expan>un<ex>d</ex></expan> die <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan> und auch ire
                        güter noch <expan>sich<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wollet auf
                                <expan>freuntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> recht, als etc. Das
                                <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. Und het ir
                            <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> czu <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>H<ex>einrich</ex></expan> Rumel <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dheine<ex>m</ex></expan> der <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> burgern, icht <expan>cze
                                spreche<ex>n</ex></expan>, <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir euch <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>m</expan>
<expan>scheimbote<ex>n</ex></expan> mit <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>m</expan>
<expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalt <expan>unv<ex>er</ex></expan>czogens
                        slewnigs <expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>
<expan>helffe<ex>n,</ex></expan>
<expan>wen<ex>n</ex></expan> wir des <expan>erma<ex>n</ex>t</expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>den,</expan> so <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, czu <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> ir
                            <expan>czu spreche<ex>n</ex></expan> habt, anheim sind, <expan>on
                                gev<ex>er</ex>d</expan>. Antwurt. </ab>
</div>
